ZH: 我需要申请一个签证才能够出国旅行。
EN: I need to apply for a visa in order to travel abroad.

ZH: 我的签证明年就要过期了，我得尽快续签。
EN: My visa will expire next year, I need to renew it as soon as possible.

ZH: 他已经拿到了工作签证，可以开始在外国工作了。
EN: He has obtained a work visa and can start working abroad.

ZH: 我们需要一份旅游签证才能够参加这个旅行团。
EN: We need a tourist visa in order to join this tour group.

ZH: 他们正在等待签证的批准结果。
EN: They are waiting for the approval result of their visa.

ZH: 她的签证申请被拒绝了，她很失望。
EN: Her visa application was rejected, she was disappointed.

ZH: 这个国家对旅游签证有一些特殊的要求。
EN: This country has some specific requirements for tourist visas.

ZH: 我们需要提供护照和一份填写完整的签证申请表格。
EN: We need to provide our passports and a completed visa application form.

ZH: 我们需要支付签证费用才能够获得签证。
EN: We need to pay the visa fee in order to obtain the visa.

ZH: 他正在办理探亲签证，希望能够尽快见到自己的家人。
EN: He is processing a family visit visa, hoping to see his family as soon as possible.

ZH: 这个签证的有效期为三个月。
EN: The validity period of this visa is three months.

ZH: 我们需要提供机票预订证明作为签证申请的支持文件。
EN: We need to provide the proof of flight booking as supporting documents for visa application.

ZH: 我需要一个休闲签证以便在国外度假。
EN: I need a leisure visa in order to have a vacation abroad.

ZH: 我们需要预约一个签证面试。
EN: We need to make an appointment for a visa interview.

ZH: 他正在努力准备签证面试的材料。
EN: He is working hard to prepare the documents for the visa interview.

ZH: 这个国家对于某些国家的公民免签证。
EN: This country waives visas for citizens of certain countries.

ZH: 我需要签证处的联系方式，以便咨询一些问题。
EN: I need the contact information of the visa office in order to inquire about some questions.

ZH: 他的工作签证正在加急处理中。
EN: His work visa is being processed urgently.

ZH: 政府正在努力简化签证程序，以吸引更多的外国游客。
EN: The government is working hard to simplify the visa process in order to attract more foreign tourists.

ZH: 考虑到签证的办理时间，我们需要尽早开始准备签证材料。
EN: Considering the processing time of the visa, we need to start preparing the visa documents as early as possible.
